comments: Paul's (PHX) left hand comes forward and marginal contact occurs with McCollum's (NOP) back after his gather.
Marshall (NOP) and Craig (PHX) each make clean contact with the ball as they pursue the rebound.
Williamson (NOP) brings his left arm forward and marginal contact occurs with Craig's (PHX) front/left arm, causing Craig to momentarily lose control of the ball, which he quickly recovers.
Williamson's (NOP) right leg is extended to the side when body contact occurs during Craig's (PHX) upward shooting motion, affecting his shot attempt near the rim.
Paul (PHX) engages and disengages with Murphy III (NOP) as Murphy III moves to set the pick.
Ayton (PHX) is in the paint for at or about three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Craig (PHX) is moving laterally and makes marginal body contact during Williamson's (NOP) drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Marshall's (NOP) left arm is extended to the side and marginal contact occurs with Paul's (PHX) arm as Paul rejects the pick.
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in Marshall's (NOP) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Craig (PHX) moves forward as he pursues the rebound and marginal contact occurs with Nance Jr.'s (NOP) back after Nance Jr. retrieves the ball.
Murphy III (NOP) establishes a screening position outside Craig's (PHX) field of vision and does not give a step of distance prior to the contact occurring, which Murphy III delivers.
Nance Jr. (NOP) makes clean forearm contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Lee (PHX) at the end of the drive.
Lee (PHX) engages and disengages with McCollum (NOP) off-ball.
Nance Jr. (NOP) establishes himself in Lee's (PHX) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Ayton (PHX) extends his right arm forward and initiates contact across Williamson's (NOP) right arm after his gather.
Paul (PHX) gives a step of distance prior to contact occurring with Williamson (NOP) during the screen, which Paul does not deliver.
Landale (PHX) establishes himself in Daniels' (NOP) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Landale (PHX) is firming up over his right foot and absorbs the contact made with Daniels (NOP) as the pick is set.
Nance Jr. (NOP) is moving forward slightly prior to marginal body contact occurring with Paul (PHX) along the sideline.
Paul (PHX) brings his right arm toward Nance Jr.'s (NOP) right side and marginal contact occurs as Paul pivots toward the perimeter.
Marshall (NOP) initiates contact with Lee's (PHX) right arm and side as Lee receives the pass.
Bridges (PHX) and Landale (PHX) move forward slightly prior to marginal contact occurring with McCollum's (NOP) arm/front as he splits the double team.
Paul (PHX) brings his arms forward slightly prior to marginal contact occurring with McCollum's (NOP) front as he elevates to pass.
McCollum (NOP) releases the pass prior to his right foot returning to the floor.
Paul (PHX) commits a take foul on Marshall (NOP).
Landale (PHX) establishes himself in Marshall's (NOP) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Marshall (NOP) engages and disengages with Landale (PHX) as the pick expires.
Daniels (NOP) is moving alongside Paul's (PHX) path and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs as they come together during the drive.
Paul (PHX) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two steps before starting his upward shooting motion.
Daniels (NOP) legally contests Paul's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Lee (PHX) makes clean contact with the ball as simultaneous marginal contact occurs with Williamson's (NOP) side/arm when Williamson receives the pass.
Landale (PHX) legally contests Williamson's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
